@node Local revision history
@subsection Local revision history

@findex wikipedia-mirror-history-view
@findex wikipedia-mirror-history-diff
@findex wikipedia-mirror-history-refresh
The local history buffer shows revisions stored in the database for a @*
given page.  The command @code{wikipedia-mirror-history-view} (@samp{RET}, @samp{v}) @*
displays the stored wikitext of the revision at point.  The command @*
@code{wikipedia-mirror-history-diff} (@samp{d}) shows the diff between the @*
revision and its parent, using locally stored content. @*

Both commands require that the revision content was downloaded during @*
synchronization.  If content is not available, an error is reported. @*

